items.title: Awesome Jax
items.content_text: ### Libraries / New Libraries * [Kernex (⭐71)](https://github.com/ASEM000/kernex) - Differentiable stencil decorators in JAX. * [MaxText (⭐1.8k)](https://github.com/google/maxtext) - A simple, performant and scalable Jax LLM written in pure Python/Jax and targeting Google Cloud TPUs. * [Pax (⭐513)](https://github.com/google/paxml) - A Jax-based machine learning framework for training large scale models.
items.content_html:
Libraries / New Libraries

  • Kernex (⭐71) - Differentiable stencil decorators in JAX.
  • MaxText (⭐1.8k) - A simple, performant and scalable Jax LLM written in pure Python/Jax and targeting Google Cloud TPUs.
  • Pax (⭐513) - A Jax-based machine learning framework for training large scale models.

items.title: Awesome Go
